there are saying that.it is much beautiful to find the one who can make you happy than to wait for him..
hmmm..confusing for me?..
ive been in a relationship now i though he`s faithful and honest..but i find it wrong...

hehehe so desperate....
iam broken..hu can make me okay agen?...hahaha....still finding fo my guy....the guy that will love me forever..
he doexnt care about others...will always make me feel happy...and the one who really care`s for me...



asan kan ba?!...

haaayy...still waiting for you MR. right...

uhmm....how to start ?!...hehehe...ok

there`s a point in our lives that we have to face tough dicisions...sometimes at sum points we dont know how to deal with this stuff...

what i mean is...its hard to make a decision that the ending is nothing...
i dont know how to handle my feelings when i started to fall for a wrong person...
it`s so hard to let him go its because you still love him...
you are pretending that youre okay but in yourself you know that youre not...
when you see him, youre heart doesnt know what to do...
its so sad to let go the one you love...but you have to do it,..
you dont have choice...
you have to do it...or else you will make yourself a trying hard...
you dont need to hide those feelings...
you have to cheer up after those unforgettable heartaches....
its so painful...to let him go...but i must...
i dont know how to move on on that feelings...
its so hard...
to say goodbye...
but then i have to face it...
